yang dah jadi jaguh empat kali.

96
00:07:12,890 --> 00:07:15,393
Kamu pasti akan masuk syurga.

97
00:07:15,476 --> 00:07:18,271
Hei, kamu patut risaukan
diri kamu sendiri.

98
00:07:18,354 --> 00:07:20,648
Kamu nampak tak kereta Jin-su?

99
00:07:20,731 --> 00:07:23,109
Keretanya lebih mahal daripada gaji kamu.

100
00:07:23,192 --> 00:07:24,152
Fikirlah sikit.

101
00:07:24,235 --> 00:07:27,363
Ini bukan soal Jin-su saja.

102
00:07:27,447 --> 00:07:30,241
Saya tak pernah menang.
Layakkah jadi jurulatih?

103
00:07:30,324 --> 00:07:32,994
Abang dah cakap itu tak penting.

104
00:07:33,077 --> 00:07:34,829
Kamu memang tak faham bahasa.

105
00:07:38,541 --> 00:07:39,542
Dengar sini.

106
00:07:40,376 --> 00:07:43,504
Ayah banyak kali menang kejohanan,

107
00:07:44,130 --> 00:07:47,341
tapi dia tak ada bakat jadi jurulatih.

108
00:07:47,425 --> 00:07:51,512
Kebolehan menyampaikan maklumat
supaya orang lain faham.

109
00:07:51,596 --> 00:07:54,891
Hei, apa namanya?
Bantu orang memahami sesuatu.

110
00:07:54,974 --> 00:07:56,893
Mengajar. Ayah tak pandai mengajar.

111
00:07:56,976 --> 00:07:59,812
Ya. Mengajar. Pengajar.

112
00:08:00,313 --> 00:08:01,856
- "Jar"?
- Ya, itu.

113
00:08:01,939 --> 00:08:05,693
Apa pun, terima sajalah tawaran itu.

114
00:08:05,776 --> 00:08:07,445
Ini peluang yang baik!

115
00:08:07,528 --> 00:08:09,405
Aduhai. Sudahlah.

116
00:08:10,072 --> 00:08:13,701
Jangan cuba yakinkan saya.
Saya dah buat keputusan.

117
00:08:13,784 --> 00:08:16,329
Kamu akan mati kesejukan dan kelaparan!

118
00:08:16,412 --> 00:08:17,580
Hei!

119
00:08:18,581 --> 00:08:20,917
Apa nak buat dengan si bengap itu?

120
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:22,084
Biarlah dia.

121
00:08:22,168 --> 00:08:25,129
Dia boleh buat strim langsung dengan saya.

122
00:08:28,424 --> 00:08:30,426
Peliknya.

123
00:08:31,344 --> 00:08:33,012
Ke mana perginya pita itu?

124
00:08:33,095 --> 00:08:35,056
Semua ada kecuali yang itu.

125
00:08:35,139 --> 00:08:37,308
Kamu cari apa dari tadi?

126
00:08:37,391 --> 00:08:41,354
Ingat tak rakaman kali pertama
abang menang kejohanan?

127
00:08:41,437 --> 00:08:43,564
- Saya nak tengok balik.
- Okey.

128
00:08:43,648 --> 00:08:46,859
Tapi pita itu saja yang hilang.

129
00:08:46,943 --> 00:08:49,862
- Abang ada ambil?
- Tidak. Abang pun tak tahu.

130
00:08:50,613 --> 00:08:51,739
Baek-du!

131
00:08:53,157 --> 00:08:54,742
Peliknya.

132
00:08:57,870 --> 00:09:00,206
Ada sesuatu yang saya tak faham.

133
00:09:00,790 --> 00:09:06,295
Kenapa Choi Chil-seong pergi
ke luar bandar ketika dia masih diburu?

134
00:09:06,379 --> 00:09:10,841
Kalau saya, tentu saya dah bawa duit
lari ke luar negara dan bersembunyi.

135
00:09:10,925 --> 00:09:14,637
Tabiat lama sukar diubah.
Mungkin dia cuba cari makan di sini.

136
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:18,182
Di perlawanan ssireum kampung?
Selepas perlawanan besar?

137
00:09:18,933 --> 00:09:20,768
Jatuhlah air muka dia nanti.

138
00:09:21,727 --> 00:09:24,730
Lagipun Choi Chil-seong dah mati.

139
00:09:24,814 --> 00:09:26,983
- Jadi…
- Jadi pergilah balik.

140
00:09:27,066 --> 00:09:29,026
Saya tak suruh ikut saya ke sini.

141
00:09:29,110 --> 00:09:30,861
Awak sangka saya nak datang?

142
00:09:30,945 --> 00:09:32,989
Saya datang atas arahan Puan Chu.

143
00:09:33,072 --> 00:09:36,075
Bahagianya suami isteri ini.

144
00:09:38,160 --> 00:09:38,995
Hei.

145
00:09:39,787 --> 00:09:43,374
Kamu rasa berapa lama
kamu boleh bertahan di sini?

146
00:09:44,709 --> 00:09:45,960
Kemas sajalah barang.

147
00:09:46,043 --> 00:09:48,796
Ikut saya balik ke Seoul nanti.

148
00:09:51,173 --> 00:09:54,093
Jadi apa yang awak cuba sampaikan?

149
00:09:54,176 --> 00:09:55,803
Awak nak buat apa?

150
00:09:55,886 --> 00:09:58,222
Masih belum terlambat untuk menyiasat

151
00:09:58,306 --> 00:10:00,099
- secara terbuka…
- Tak boleh.

152
00:10:01,434 --> 00:10:04,937
Kita perlu tahu kenapa Choi datang
ke Geosan, dia jumpa siapa

153
00:10:05,021 --> 00:10:06,439
dan siapa bunuh dia.

154
00:10:08,357 --> 00:10:11,485
Yu-gyeong, awak betul-betul yakin?

155
00:10:11,569 --> 00:10:14,030
Awak yakin awak boleh siasat semua itu?

156
00:10:16,282 --> 00:10:17,283
Ya.

157
00:10:20,620 --> 00:10:21,621
Yakah?

158
00:10:22,246 --> 00:10:23,789
- Okey, cubalah.
- Puan.

159
00:10:23,873 --> 00:10:26,250
Kamu tak dapat menyamar lama-lama.

160
00:10:26,334 --> 00:10:30,087
Jadi cari lejar Choi
atau suspek pembunuhan secepat mungkin.

161
00:10:30,171 --> 00:10:31,172
Faham?

162
00:10:35,718 --> 00:10:38,596
Ini semua salah Oh Du-sik.

163
00:10:38,679 --> 00:10:41,349
Sekarang, saya yang susah.

164
00:10:41,432 --> 00:10:44,852
Dia memang sengaja nak kenakan saya.

165
00:10:44,935 --> 00:10:48,439
Tentu dia dah lama rancang…

166
00:10:58,616 --> 00:11:00,034
Mak cik itu…

167
00:11:06,582 --> 00:11:08,084
Gelung asap?

168
00:11:12,588 --> 00:11:15,257
Tapi dia buat apa di sini?

169
00:11:15,341 --> 00:11:17,510
Betul juga kata Hyeon-uk.

170
00:11:17,593 --> 00:11:20,471
Kalau masih tak jumpa apa-apa,
pulanglah ke Seoul.

171
00:11:20,554 --> 00:11:21,555
Baik.

172
00:11:22,807 --> 00:11:26,894
Hyeon-uk, awasi dia.
Kalau dia mengamuk lagi, hubungi saya.

173
00:11:26,977 --> 00:11:28,396
Baik, puan.

174
00:11:29,105 --> 00:11:30,272
Kamu berdua

175
00:11:31,357 --> 00:11:33,275
tak bergaduh setiap hari, bukan?

176
00:11:33,359 --> 00:11:34,527
- Tak, puan.
- Tak.

177
00:11:35,069 --> 00:11:38,072
Jangan buat hal. Saya sentiasa memerhati.

178
00:11:39,990 --> 00:11:44,787
Kamu berdua buat saya risau.

179
00:11:49,583 --> 00:11:52,795
Jangan ikut saya.
Buat pening kepala saya saja.

180
00:11:53,337 --> 00:11:55,297
- Baik.
- Semoga selamat sampai.

181
00:11:55,381 --> 00:11:56,298
Masuklah.

182
00:12:06,434 --> 00:12:08,352
Bodoh.

183
00:12:08,436 --> 00:12:10,813
Kenapa biar dia mengarah-arahkan awak?

184
00:12:15,651 --> 00:12:17,319
Saya rasa macam tak percaya.

185
00:12:17,820 --> 00:12:19,363
Tak masuk akal langsung!

186
00:12:19,447 --> 00:12:22,408
Sekarang Jin-su tiada hala tuju.

187
00:12:22,992 --> 00:12:24,660
Kelakar juga sebenarnya.

188
00:12:25,161 --> 00:12:27,204
Tapi Jin-su tak patut balik

189
00:12:27,288 --> 00:12:29,957
selepas berbincang sekali saja
dengan Park.

190
00:12:30,040 --> 00:12:32,543
- Dia patut tandatangan kontrak dulu…
- Apa?

191
00:12:34,670 --> 00:12:35,921
Hei, dengar sini.

192
00:12:36,005 --> 00:12:38,924
Manalah dia tahu keadaan akan jadi begini?

193
00:12:39,008 --> 00:12:43,554
Dia datang sebab ketua jurulatih
merayu supaya dia terima tawaran itu.

194
00:12:43,637 --> 00:12:47,683
Jin-su tak buat salah.
Dia cuma terlalu lembut hati!

195
00:12:47,766 --> 00:12:49,768
Saya tak cakap dia buat salah.

196
00:12:49,852 --> 00:12:52,354
Kalau Jin-su tak boleh jadi jurulatih…

197
00:12:54,315 --> 00:12:56,734
Kenapa tak boleh?

198
00:12:56,817 --> 00:13:00,988
Dia serba-serbi lebih bagus
daripada Baek-du. Kenapa tak boleh?

199
00:13:01,071 --> 00:13:02,364
Kenapa cakap begitu?

200
00:13:02,448 --> 00:13:04,492
Sebab itu saya cakap, "kalau".

201
00:13:04,575 --> 00:13:07,703
Sudahlah. Takutlah saya nak cakap apa-apa.

202
00:13:07,786 --> 00:13:09,830
Kenapa mesti Baek-du?

203
00:13:11,790 --> 00:13:13,042
Saya tak nak makan.

204
00:13:13,125 --> 00:13:15,503
- Duduk!
- Okey, saya makan.

205
00:13:19,965 --> 00:13:21,717
- Helo.
- Hei.

206
00:13:22,426 --> 00:13:25,721
Tak sangka jadi begini, bukan?

207
00:13:26,764 --> 00:13:28,974
Mari bincang di dalam. Masuklah.

208
00:13:29,058 --> 00:13:30,559
Mari.

209
00:13:32,895 --> 00:13:36,065
Pengurus kami tak cakap apa-apa pun
sebelum ini.

210
00:13:36,148 --> 00:13:39,026
Kemudian tiba-tiba dia sebut nama Baek-du.

211
00:13:39,693 --> 00:13:41,904
- Duduklah.
- Okey.

212
00:13:43,072 --> 00:13:45,950
Aduhai. Kenapa dia tak cakap awal-awal?

213
00:13:46,033 --> 00:13:47,868
Sebelum saya panggil awak ke sini.

214
00:13:47,952 --> 00:13:49,578
Pengurus besar baru?

215
00:13:49,662 --> 00:13:51,455
Apa? Ya.

216
00:13:51,539 --> 00:13:53,791
Pengurus baru yang dilantik oleh gabenor.

217
00:13:53,874 --> 00:13:55,125
Gabenor?

218
00:13:55,209 --> 00:13:57,253
Dia direkrut dari pasukan lain?

219
00:13:57,336 --> 00:14:01,257
Saya tak tahu.
Mungkin ada orang minta bantuan gabenor.

220
00:14:02,800 --> 00:14:05,886
Tapi dia agak berbakat dalam ssireum.

221
00:14:06,470 --> 00:14:10,015
Pada hari pertama,
salah seorang pemain tak puas hati

222
00:14:10,099 --> 00:14:12,017
dan dia humban pemain itu ke tanah.

223
00:14:12,601 --> 00:14:14,562
Apa? Siapa nama dia?

224
00:14:15,145 --> 00:14:16,855
Yu-gyeong. Oh Yu-gyeong.

225
00:14:17,606 --> 00:14:19,358
- Perempuan?
- Ya.

226
00:14:20,025 --> 00:14:23,237
Gabenor berkali-kali minta kami

227
00:14:23,320 --> 00:14:25,739
beri kerjasama dengan pengurus baru.

228
00:14:25,823 --> 00:14:27,741
Jadi saya mesti dengar pendapatnya.

229
00:14:30,911 --> 00:14:33,998
Saya akan cuba yakinkan dia.

230
00:14:34,081 --> 00:14:36,959
Beri saya masa beberapa hari, okey?

231
00:15:03,527 --> 00:15:06,363
Jangan sebut "hai-yah". Mereka tahulah.

232
00:15:10,117 --> 00:15:11,327
