di stesen kereta api bawah tanah

947
00:56:43,191 --> 00:56:46,736
dan turun padang untuk menyiasat
dan mengumpul maklumat.

948
00:56:46,820 --> 00:56:48,738
Mata penyeluk saku biasanya

949
00:56:48,822 --> 00:56:50,532
memerhatikan barang yang dibawa

950
00:56:50,615 --> 00:56:53,118
seperti beg tangan dan bukan orang ramai.

951
00:56:53,201 --> 00:56:55,662
Mata mereka juga biasanya melilau.

952
00:56:55,745 --> 00:56:57,372
Kadangkala mereka duduk lama

953
00:56:57,455 --> 00:57:00,166
dan hanya bergerak apabila stesen sesak.

954
00:57:06,381 --> 00:57:10,176
Bedebah itu panggil nama saya
dengan begitu biadab.

955
00:57:10,844 --> 00:57:14,597
Saya selamatkan dia daripada ditikam
dan begitu dia layan saya?

956
00:57:18,768 --> 00:57:22,230
Kita tak ada masa.
Mereka tak dapat tutup mulut lama-lama.

957
00:57:22,313 --> 00:57:23,857
Kita mesti cepat bertindak.

958
00:57:24,566 --> 00:57:26,651
Berita cepat tersebar.

959
00:57:29,821 --> 00:57:32,490
Kamu boleh pergi. Saya nak merokok dulu.

960
00:57:33,783 --> 00:57:35,368
- Baik.
- Baik, puan.

961
00:57:38,204 --> 00:57:39,456
Kamu pun baliklah.

962
00:57:39,539 --> 00:57:40,999
- Puan.
- Baik.

963
00:57:41,082 --> 00:57:42,667
Saya nak beritahu sesuatu.

964
00:57:44,127 --> 00:57:45,044
Pergilah dulu.

965
00:57:51,217 --> 00:57:54,095
Kalau seorang saja balik awal,

966
00:57:55,054 --> 00:57:58,475
biasanya yang lain akan mengumpat dia.

967
00:58:00,935 --> 00:58:03,313
Dia suruh saya balik
sebab nak mengata saya.

968
00:58:04,314 --> 00:58:07,025
Tak matang betul. Dia memang…

969
00:58:07,984 --> 00:58:09,152
Apa lagi kali ini?

970
00:58:12,655 --> 00:58:15,742
Dia buat apa di sini?
Dia patut makan tauhu di rumah.

971
00:58:16,951 --> 00:58:17,785
Hei!

972
00:58:18,286 --> 00:58:21,331
Kenapa lambat sangat balik?
Lama saya tunggu awak.

973
00:58:22,248 --> 00:58:24,709
Kenapa? Awak nak cakap sesuatu?

974
00:58:24,792 --> 00:58:26,336
Awak tahu tak…

975
00:58:26,961 --> 00:58:27,921
Tidak.

976
00:58:29,422 --> 00:58:30,590
Saya nak cakap sikit.

977
00:58:32,467 --> 00:58:33,676
Awak nak cakap apa?

978
00:58:35,136 --> 00:58:37,388
Saya nak cakap…

979
00:58:39,098 --> 00:58:40,683
tentang Yu-gyeong.

980
00:58:40,767 --> 00:58:42,519
Oh Yu-gyeong? Ada apa?

981
00:58:44,896 --> 00:58:46,397
Puan tahu sesuatu, bukan?

982
00:58:47,065 --> 00:58:48,900
Saya? Tahu apa?

983
00:58:48,983 --> 00:58:50,944
Sebab Yu-gyeong datang ke sini.

984
00:58:52,111 --> 00:58:54,489
Bukan sebab itu
puan luluskan siasatan ini?

985
00:58:55,448 --> 00:58:59,994
Puan tahu rancangan ini agak berbahaya.

986
00:59:00,078 --> 00:59:01,746
Apa maksud awak?

987
00:59:03,122 --> 00:59:05,250
Kenapa awak fikir begitu?

988
00:59:05,917 --> 00:59:07,168
Ada apa-apa berlaku?

989
00:59:07,794 --> 00:59:10,838
Tak ada apa-apa. Cuma…

990
00:59:12,006 --> 00:59:13,383
Keadaan agak…

991
00:59:15,134 --> 00:59:18,555
Puan tahu Kim Baek-du
yang disoal di sini tadi?

992
00:59:18,638 --> 00:59:20,056
Ya. Kenapa dengan dia?

993
00:59:21,057 --> 00:59:23,393
Saya rasa ada sesuatu di antara

994
00:59:24,352 --> 00:59:25,979
dia dan Yu-gyeong.

995
00:59:28,481 --> 00:59:29,566
Aduh, kenapa…

996
00:59:29,649 --> 00:59:31,484
- Kuatnya awak.
- Cepatlah.

997
00:59:31,568 --> 00:59:33,111
- Saya boleh…
- Cepat.

998
00:59:33,194 --> 00:59:34,362
Lepaskan saya!

999
00:59:35,280 --> 00:59:37,407
Kuatnya awak.

1000
00:59:39,033 --> 00:59:40,326
Apa hal?

1001
00:59:41,119 --> 00:59:42,829
Cakaplah cepat.

1002
00:59:43,830 --> 00:59:45,665
Saya tahu

1003
00:59:45,748 --> 00:59:49,127
ini agak mengejutkan, tapi…

1004
00:59:49,210 --> 00:59:50,211
Tapi apa?

1005
00:59:51,004 --> 00:59:51,921
Awak pun tahu

1006
00:59:52,547 --> 00:59:55,258
kita membesar bersama.

1007
00:59:55,341 --> 00:59:58,511
Kita ada banyak kenangan bersama.
Betul tak?

1008
01:00:00,430 --> 01:00:04,142
Awak nak cakap apa sebenarnya?

1009
01:00:06,352 --> 01:00:07,520
Du-sik.

1010
01:00:10,898 --> 01:00:11,899
Awak…

1011
01:00:15,653 --> 01:00:16,613
Awak…

1012
01:00:20,199 --> 01:00:23,202
Maksud awak, hubungan cinta?

1013
01:00:26,039 --> 01:00:28,625
Dia ada masa nak bercinta
dalam situasi ini?

1014
01:00:28,708 --> 01:00:30,543
Bukan itu maksud saya.

1015
01:00:31,252 --> 01:00:33,963
Puan dan Yu-gyeong sama saja.

1016
01:00:34,047 --> 01:00:34,922
Jadi apa?

1017
01:00:35,006 --> 01:00:37,258
Saya cuma rasa

1018
01:00:38,134 --> 01:00:41,346
mereka dah lama kenal.

1019
01:00:41,429 --> 01:00:43,097
Mereka dah lama kenal?

1020
01:00:43,181 --> 01:00:45,767
Ya. Jadi saya cuma risau

1021
01:00:45,850 --> 01:00:48,853
Baek-du mungkin akan dapat tahu
tujuan kita ke sini.

1022
01:00:48,936 --> 01:00:50,271
Tak mungkin.

1023
01:00:50,813 --> 01:00:55,735
Saya perhatikan dia tadi.
Dia nampak lurus.

1024
01:00:55,818 --> 01:00:58,279
Ya, tapi…

1025
01:01:00,198 --> 01:01:02,950
Orang macam dia kadang-kadang tajam akal.

1026
01:01:04,410 --> 01:01:06,329
Luaran nampak lurus,

1027
01:01:07,163 --> 01:01:09,415
tapi hakikatnya, naluri mereka kuat.

1028
01:01:13,211 --> 01:01:14,462
Awak…

1029
01:01:17,090 --> 01:01:18,216
poliskah?

1030
01:01:20,343 --> 01:01:21,594
- Betul, bukan?
- Apa?

1031
01:01:23,554 --> 01:01:25,390
Saya boleh agak dari wajah awak.

1032
01:01:25,473 --> 01:01:26,724
Awak polis.

1033
01:01:26,808 --> 01:01:28,893
Macam mana awak…

1034
01:01:28,976 --> 01:01:31,854
Macam mana awak tahu?

1035
01:01:31,938 --> 01:01:34,107
Itu pentingkah?

1036
01:01:34,190 --> 01:01:35,191
Pentinglah.

1037
01:01:36,401 --> 01:01:40,488
Jadi macam mana awak dapat tahu?

1038
01:01:42,281 --> 01:01:43,366
Ibu mentua awak.

1039
01:01:44,325 --> 01:01:46,411
Saya kenal dia.

1040
01:01:48,246 --> 01:01:49,539
Mi-suk.

1041
01:01:50,331 --> 01:01:51,791
Idola awak.

1042
01:01:54,043 --> 01:01:56,879
Kenapa? Awak terkejut?

1043
01:01:57,463 --> 01:01:59,590
Saya ada satu lagi soalan untuk awak.

1044
01:02:03,678 --> 01:02:04,887
Du-sik.

1045
01:02:07,348 --> 01:02:08,683
Awak…

1046
01:02:10,685 --> 01:02:12,186
Awak…

1047
01:02:17,775 --> 01:02:19,110
belum kahwin, bukan?

1048
01:02:21,070 --> 01:02:22,071
Apa?

1049
01:02:24,031 --> 01:02:26,200
Orang yang nalurinya kuat

1050
01:02:26,951 --> 01:02:29,078
susah ditipu.

1051
01:02:33,666 --> 01:02:36,294
LIKE FLOWERS IN SAND

1052
01:03:00,067 --> 01:03:01,402
Saya, Kim Baek-du,

1053
01:03:01,486 --> 01:03:04,530
akan kembali ke Pasukan Ssireum Geosan-gun

1054
01:03:04,614 --> 01:03:05,531
mulai hari ini!

1055
01:03:05,615 --> 01:03:07,074
Ayuh!

1056
01:03:07,158 --> 01:03:08,493
Kim Baek-du!

1057
01:03:08,576 --> 01:03:12,163
Buat apa awak kembali
kalau asas pun awak tak tahu?

1058
01:03:12,246 --> 01:03:15,500
Kemalangan di takungan air itu
baru saja berlalu.

1059
01:03:15,583 --> 01:03:17,084
Ada khabar angin aneh.

1060
01:03:17,168 --> 01:03:18,252
Saya dengar

1061
01:03:18,336 --> 01:03:21,380
jurulatih minta Dong-seok
sengaja biar Baek-du menang.

1062
01:03:21,464 --> 01:03:22,840
Awak tahu?

1063
01:03:22,924 --> 01:03:26,844
Apa yang berlaku di kampung ini?

1064
01:03:28,721 --> 01:03:30,723
Terjemahan sari kata oleh Aimi Farhana

